# VincentTim (tim.exe) scratch output: "<input>.<n>.meta/.png/.palette.png"
# left next to the working directory by an interrupted export. The normal
# pipeline keeps these under temp_vincent_tim/ and cleans up after itself;
# these patterns just make sure a stray one can never be committed.
